A snapshot of each sensor taken when the error occurred is shown below.
	<% @alert.snapshot.each do |sensor| %> 
	-Sensor #<%= sensor['id'] %> (<%= sensor['friendly_id'] %>)
	-Type: <%= sensor['category'] %>
	-Model: <%= sensor['model'] %>
	-Manufacturer: <%= sensor['manufacturer'] %>
